            <a class='permalink column-permalink' id='column_87gc' title='Col. 87GC &mdash; HL Deb 12 May 1999 vol 600 c87GC' name='column_87gc' href='#column_87gc' rel='bookmark'>87GC</a>
            those additional inspectorates. We need that flexibility, which is why the subsection is included. It is no more complicated than that.
          </p>
        </blockquote>
      </div>
      
      <div class='hentry member_contribution' id='S5LV0600P0-04656'>
        <a name='S5LV0600P0_19990512_GCR_106'>  </a>
        <blockquote cite='http://hansard.millbanksystems.com/people/ms-sally-hamwee' class='contribution_text entry-content'>
