        <a class='permalink column-permalink' id='column_104gc' title='Col. 104GC &mdash; HL Deb 12 May 1999 vol 600 c104GC' name='column_104gc' href='#column_104gc' rel='bookmark'>104GC</a>
        I thought that should be explicit rather than implicit and that is the only reason for that amendment. I beg to move.
