      </p>
      
      <p class='procedural' id='S5LV0600P0-04765'>
        <a class='permalink' href='#S5LV0600P0_19990512_GCR_215' title='Link to this contribution' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
        <span class="member">Lord Dixon-Smith</span> moved Amendment No.110:
      </p>
      
      <p class='procedural' id='S5LV0600P0-04766'>
        <a class='permalink' href='#S5LV0600P0_19990512_GCR_216' title='Link to this contribution' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
