        The noble Lord said: This is a fairly standard request to include in consultation. Clause 30(4) states:
        <q>The Secretary of State may by regulations make provision</q>
      </p>
      <a class='permalink column-permalink' id='column_105gc' title='Col. 105GC &mdash; HL Deb 12 May 1999 vol 600 c105GC' name='column_105gc' href='#column_105gc' rel='bookmark'>105GC</a>
      <p class='procedural' id='S5LV0600P0-04768'>
